<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Resumen de Vencimientos SST - {{companyName}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #0f172a;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #0f172a;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .main-table {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .header-logo {
      padding: 20px 0 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo-img {
      max-height: 48px;
      width: auto;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .card {
      background-color: #1e293b;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      margin: 0 15px;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0d9488;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .content-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .highlight-name {
      color: #0d9488;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    /* Section Styles */
    .section-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 6px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #0d9488;
    }
    
    /* Table Styles */
    .table-container {
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .data-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .data-table th {
      background-color: #0f172a;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .data-table td {
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
      color: #f1f5f9;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .data-table tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
    }
    
    /* Badge Styles */
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .badge-danger {
      background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
      color: #f87171;
      border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
    }
    .badge-warning {
      background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15);
      color: #fbbf24;
      border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 35px 0 15px 0;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488 0%, #0f766e 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 26px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.3);
    }
    .footer-signature {
      border-top: 1px solid #334155;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 25px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .signature-team {
      color: #0d9488;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .footer-info {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #64748b;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer-info a {
      color: #0d9488;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <table class="main-table" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td class="header-logo">
          <a href="https://wappy.club" target="_blank">
            <img class="logo-img" src="https://wappy.club/assets/logo.png" alt="WAPPY IA">
          </a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <div class="card">
            <h1 class="title">Hola, <span class="highlight-name">{{name}}</span></h1>
            <div class="subtitle">Somos SST — Reporte de Vencimientos</div>
            <p class="content-text">Hemos realizado el monitoreo diario para la empresa <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>. A continuación, te presentamos el resumen de los vencimientos y actividades críticas de seguridad y salud en el trabajo detectadas:</p>
            
            {{#if hasMedicalAlerts}}
            <div class="section-title">🏥 Exámenes Médicos y Seguimientos</div>
            <div class="table-container">
              <table class="data-table">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Trabajador</th>
                    <th>Cargo</th>
                    <th>Alerta</th>
                    <th>Fecha</th>
                    <th>Estado</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  {{#each medicalAlerts}}
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>{{workerName}}</strong></td>
                    <td>{{cargo}}</td>
                    <td>{{alertType}}</td>
                    <td>{{date}}</td>
                    <td><span class="badge {{statusClass}}">{{statusText}}</span></td>
                  </tr>
                  {{/each}}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if hasHeightsAlerts}}
            <div class="section-title">🪜 Cursos de Alturas</div>
            <div class="table-container">
              <table class="data-table">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Trabajador</th>
                    <th>Cargo</th>
                    <th>Certificación</th>
                    <th>Fecha</th>
                    <th>Estado</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  {{#each heightsAlerts}}
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>{{workerName}}</strong></td>
                    <td>{{cargo}}</td>
                    <td>{{courseType}}</td>
                    <td>{{date}}</td>
                    <td><span class="badge {{statusClass}}">{{statusText}}</span></td>
                  </tr>
                  {{/each}}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if hasDocAlerts}}
            <div class="section-title">🚗 Vehículos y Licencias</div>
            <div class="table-container">
              <table class="data-table">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Trabajador</th>
                    <th>Documento / Licencia</th>
                    <th>Fecha Vto.</th>
                    <th>Estado</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  {{#each docAlerts}}
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>{{workerName}}</strong></td>
                    <td>{{docType}}</td>
                    <td>{{date}}</td>
                    <td><span class="badge {{statusClass}}">{{statusText}}</span></td>
                  </tr>
                  {{/each}}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if hasTrainingAlerts}}
            <div class="section-title">📅 Capacitaciones Programadas</div>
            <div class="table-container">
              <table class="data-table">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Tema / Actividad</th>
                    <th>Responsable</th>
                    <th>Fecha Programada</th>
                    <th>Alerta</th>
                    <th>Estado</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  {{#each trainingAlerts}}
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>{{topic}}</strong></td>
                    <td>{{responsible}}</td>
                    <td>{{date}}</td>
                    <td>{{alertType}}</td>
                    <td><span class="badge {{statusClass}}">{{statusText}}</span></td>
                  </tr>
                  {{/each}}
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <p class="content-text" style="margin-top: 30px;">Te sugerimos ingresar al portal de Somos SST para programar las actualizaciones de datos, renovaciones de exámenes, o registrar la ejecución de las capacitaciones pendientes.</p>

            <div class="btn-container">
              <a href="https://wappy.club" target="_blank" class="btn">Ir al portal Somos SST</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-signature">
              Un abrazo,<br>
              <span class="signature-team">El equipo de WAPPY IA</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="footer-info">
          <p>© {{year}} WAPPY IA. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://wappy.club" target="_blank">Sitio Web</a> • 
            <a href="mailto:soporte@wappy.club">Soporte técnico</a>
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
